    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains untouched by time; the leather is supple with no creasing, and it still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is flawless, having been strictly garage-kept and maintained with an open-checkbook policy. Every service record is documented, all original keys and manuals are included, and the undercarriage is as clean as the body. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a definitive example of the model.",
      "price": 46500.0,
