      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unrivaled caliber. This vehicle has been maintained to an exacting standard, preserved in a state that transcends the typical secondary market offering. Every surface remains in pristine condition, reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship and climate-controlled storage. Mechanically, the vehicle performs with the precision of its original factory specifications. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than aesthetic and functional perfection, this remains an exemplary acquisition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
