      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car, and it shows in every single detail. It\u2019s in truly pristine, flawless condition, inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
