    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3 in impeccable factory configuration. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that remains whisper-quiet. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers crisp, short-throw engagement, paired with a perfectly calibrated M-Variable differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. Underneath, the chassis is flawless; the rear subframe has been proactively inspected and reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. Every bushing, damper, and control arm remains in peak operating condition, preserving the communicative steering feel and balanced weight distribution this platform is renowned for. This is a turn-key mechanical masterpiece, free of any VANOS rattle or subframe fatigue, finished in a preservation-level aesthetic.",
